      "file_path": "kubernetes/common/common/templates/_name.tpl",
      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 26,
      "message": "elasticsearch chart has a lot of different components and thus use in the same folder several deployment.yaml and pvc.yaml (one per component).\nAs such, Alexander wants to be able to name them differently (onap-es-component-one, onap-es-component-two, ...)\nOther solution would be to create subcharts but I'm not sure it would worth it (and I think we may need it in the future when we have several PVC/PV to create for one component ;) )",
